{"tid":920722,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本酒店到底洗唔洗比tips","createTime":"2018-11-29T04:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T16:07:59.000Z","uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"66a3d2add8cfab931aff0ca4be9208043734dc29","tid":920722,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"早幾日去完關西，有個女員工幫我拎左行李上房，本身都聽過下日本係唔興收tips，但因為我件行李都幾重下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，覺得唔好意思都係象徵式比下，拎1000yen比佢果陣，佢竟然話唔洗比番我，果下都幾無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n到底係我比得太少定係日本真係唔收呀，成個trip諗左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e95966717c286da41fecdf19db5a1020fda6c8c","tid":920722,"uid":25108,"like":18,"dislike":11,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"google 下都知啦<br />\n去旅行都唔查下當地有咩要留意<br />\n真係屌你老母早死早著"},{"pid":"e25cad5e4893d4a9739e9d0f4632db68002735e8","tid":920722,"uid":2446,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"你自己咪答咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a5fe88237b8212f50d54edf2743cf0d5cc08cc","tid":920722,"uid":191815,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"你知道人地文化唔興洗俾tips你又做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人喎，骨子裡就是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cccd8465a58667d2a3c7be2307a86bb1fb7a28","tid":920722,"uid":196924,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:47:08.000Z","msg":"正常人邏輯：<br />\n聽過日本係唔興收tips + 親身經歷日本人唔收tips = 證實日本人唔興收tips<br />\n<br />\n樓豬神奇邏輯：<br />\n聽過日本係唔興收tips + 親身經歷日本人唔收tips = 繼續懷疑日本人會收tips只係自己出手太低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl